        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2506",
        "content": "Now that September has come, and all our Parliamentary duties are over, perhaps no class of Snobs are in such high feather as the Continental Snobs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
