        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2506",
        "content": "'mr Punch,--'Taking great interest in your Snob Papers, we are very anxious to know under what class of that respectable fraternity you would designate us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
